(216, 49, 'Materi di level 7\r\n\r\n1.CSS backgroun-color\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\nbody {\r\n  background-color: lightblue;\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h1&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Halaman ini mempunyai warna background light blue!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n2.CSS backgroun-color (elemen lainnya)\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\nh1 {\r\n  background-color: green;\r\n}\r\n\r\ndiv {\r\n  background-color: lightblue;\r\n}\r\n\r\np {\r\n  background-color: yellow;\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h1&gt;CSS background-color example!&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\nThis is a text inside a div element.\r\n&lt;p&gt;This paragraph has its own background color.&lt;/p&gt;\r\nWe are still in the div element.\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n3.CSS background-image\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\nbody {\r\n  background-image: url(&quot;images/paper.jpg&quot;);\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h1&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Halaman ini menggunakan gambar sebagai background!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n4.CSS background-image (gambar yang buruk)\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\nbody {\r\n  background-image: url(&quot;images/bgdesert.png&quot;);\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h1&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Teks ini tidak mudah dibaca apabila menggunakan background seperti ini.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n5.CSS backgriund-repeat\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\nbody {\r\n  background-image: url(&quot;images/gradient_bg.png&quot;);\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h1&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Perulangan background gambar yang kurang baik...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n6.CSS backgriund-repeat (halus)\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\nbody {\r\n  background-image: url(&quot;images/gradient_bg.png&quot;);\r\n  background-repeat: repeat-x;\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h1&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Pada halaman ini, perulangan background secara horizontal!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n7.CSS backgriund-repeat : no-repeat\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\nbody {\r\n  background-image: url(&quot;images/img_tree.png&quot;);\r\n  background-repeat: no-repeat;\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h1&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ini adalah contoh menggunakan background gambar.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Background gambar tampil hanya sekali, tetapi mengganggu dalam membaca!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n8.CSS backgriund-repeat : no-repeat (disudut kanan)\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\nbody {\r\n  background-image: url(&quot;images/img_tree.png&quot;);\r\n  background-repeat: no-repeat;\r\n  background-position: right top;\r\n  margin-right: 250px;\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h1&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kali ini menggunakan background gambar no repeat, dan set posisi gambar.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Sekarang posisi background gambar tidak berulang, dan posisinya tidak mengganggu teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Pada contoh ini kita juga menambahkan margin dari sisi kanan, sehingga background gambar tidak akan mengganggu teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;'),
(217, 49, 'Materi  di level 8\r\n\r\n1. CSS Border Style\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\np.dotted {border-style: dotted;}\r\np.dashed {border-style: dashed;}\r\np.solid {border-style: solid;}\r\np.double {border-style: double;}\r\np.groove {border-style: groove;}\r\np.ridge {border-style: ridge;}\r\np.inset {border-style: inset;}\r\np.outset {border-style: outset;}\r\np.none {border-style: none;}\r\np.hidden {border-style: hidden;}\r\np.mix {border-style: dotted dashed solid double;}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Properti border-style&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Properti berikut ini menunjukkan jenis-jenis tampilan border:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;dotted&quot;&gt;Border titik-titik.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;dashed&quot;&gt;Border garis putus-putus.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;solid&quot;&gt;Border garis solid.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;double&quot;&gt;Border garis double.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;groove&quot;&gt;Border 3D Groove. Efek tergantung pemilihan nilai border-color.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;ridge&quot;&gt;Border 3D ridged. Efek tergantung pemilihan nilai border-color.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;inset&quot;&gt;Border 3D inset. Efek tergantung pemilihan nilai border-color.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;outset&quot;&gt;Border 3D outset. Efek tergantung pemilihan nilai border-color.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Tidak ada border.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;hidden&quot;&gt;Border tidak tampil/hidden.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;mix&quot;&gt;Border kombinasi/campuran.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n2.CSS Border Width\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\np.one {\r\n  border-style: solid;\r\n  border-width: 5px;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.two {\r\n  border-style: solid;\r\n  border-width: medium;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.three {\r\n  border-style: dotted;\r\n  border-width: 2px;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.four {\r\n  border-style: dotted;\r\n  border-width: thick;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.five {\r\n  border-style: double;\r\n  border-width: 15px;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.six {\r\n  border-style: double;\r\n  border-width: thick;\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Properti border-width&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Properti width / lebar dari 4 sisi border:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;one&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;two&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;three&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;four&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;five&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;six&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Note:&lt;/b&gt; Properti &quot;border-width&quot; tidak akan bekerja apabila digunakan secara mandiri / tanpa menggunakan properti border utama. \r\nPastikan spesifikkan properti &quot;border-style&quot; yang digunakan terlebih dahulu.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n3.Specific Side Widths\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\np.one {\r\n  border-style: solid;\r\n  border-width: 5px 20px; \r\n  /* 5px atas dan bawah, 20px sisi kanan kiri */\r\n}\r\n\r\np.two {\r\n  border-style: solid;\r\n  border-width: 20px 5px; \r\n  /* 20px atas dan bawah, 5px sisi kanan kiri */\r\n}\r\n\r\np.three {\r\n  border-style: solid;\r\n  border-width: 25px 10px 4px 35px; \r\n  /* 25px atas, 10px kanan, 4px bawah and 35px kiri */\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Properti border-width&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Properti border-width dapat memiliki nilai dari 1 hingga 4 (untuk top border, right border, bottom border, dan left border):&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;one&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;two&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;three&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n4.CSS Border Color\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\np.one {\r\n  border-style: solid;\r\n  border-color: red;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.two {\r\n  border-style: solid;\r\n  border-color: green;\r\n} \r\n\r\np.three {\r\n  border-style: dotted;\r\n  border-color: blue;\r\n} \r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Properti border-color&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Properti ini menspesifikkan warna dari 4 sisi border:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;one&quot;&gt;Border solid merah&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;two&quot;&gt;Border solid hijau&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;three&quot;&gt;Border biru titik-titik&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Catatan:&lt;/b&gt; Properti &quot;border-color&quot; tidak akan bisa digunakan apabila berdiri sendiri. Silakan menggunakan properti &quot;border-style&quot; terlebih dahulu.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n5.Specific Side Colors\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\np.one {\r\n  border-style: solid;\r\n  border-color: red green blue yellow; /* red top, green right, blue bottom and yellow left */\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Properti border-color&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Properti border-color dapat memiliki satu hingga empat nilai (untuk top border, right border, bottom border, dan the left border):&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;one&quot;&gt;Border solid dengan warna kombinasi&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n'),
(218, 58, '&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\np.one {\r\n  border-style: solid;\r\n  border-width: 5px;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.two {\r\n  border-style: solid;\r\n  border-width: medium;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.three {\r\n  border-style: dotted;\r\n  border-width: 2px;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.four {\r\n  border-style: dotted;\r\n  border-width: thick;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.five {\r\n  border-style: double;\r\n  border-width: 15px;\r\n}\r\n\r\np.six {\r\n  border-style: double;\r\n  border-width: thick;\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Properti border-width&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Properti width / lebar dari 4 sisi border:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;one&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;two&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;three&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;four&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;five&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;six&quot;&gt;Ini adalah teks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Note:&lt;/b&gt; Properti &quot;border-width&quot; tidak akan bekerja apabila digunakan secara mandiri / tanpa menggunakan properti border utama. \r\nPastikan spesifikkan properti &quot;border-style&quot; yang digunakan terlebih dahulu.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\np.one { border-style: solid; border-width: 5px; } p.two { border-style: solid; border-width: medium; } p.three { border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; } p.four { border-style: dotted; border-width: thick; }\r\np.one { border-style: solid; border-color: red; } p.two { border-style: solid; border-color: green; } p.three { border-style: dotted; border-color: blue; }\r\n'),
(219, 58, ' p { margin-top: 100px; margin-bottom: 100px; margin-right: 150px; margin-left: 80px; }\r\np { margin: 25px 50px 75px 100px; }\r\ndiv { width: 300px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid red; }\r\ndiv { border: 1px solid red; margin-left: 100px; } p.ex1 { margin-left: inherit; }\r\n'),
(220, 54, '\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\nh1 {\r\n  background-color: green;\r\n}\r\n\r\ndiv {\r\n  background-color: lightblue;\r\n}\r\n\r\np {\r\n  background-color: yellow;\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h1&gt;CSS background-color example!&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\nThis is a text inside a div element.\r\n&lt;p&gt;This paragraph has its own background color.&lt;/p&gt;\r\nWe are still in the div element.\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n'),
